Package: clinconcept
Type: Package
Title: A package for loading and querying clinical concept dictionaries in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rob Free
Maintainer: Rob Free <rob.free@le.ac.uk>
Description: The package provides tools to build/load a database with one or more clinical
    dictionaries using UK-based downloads of these dictionaries and query/search the dictionaries using
    both hierarchical/DAG-based searches and advanced filtering.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests:
  testthat,
  RMySQL (>= 0.10),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Imports:
  dplyr (>= 0.7),
  dbplyr (>= 1.4.0),
  RSQLite (>= 2.0),
  jsonlite (>= 1.4),
  readr (>= 1.1),
  magrittr,
  methods,
  rlang,
  DBI
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1

